HEADWORD: Quinoyl
<hw>Qui"noyl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Quin</ets>one +
<ets>-yl</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A radical of which
